{
  "stem": "5375.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "On the end of the transport, there were SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were aiming only for sport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And people, the same thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Like they would aim at squirrels, or on rabbits, or whatever, and killing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "People were running from behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We stopped and they were running from there, because they were killing them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, it was a time when we started running the night-- at night [INAUDIBLE], only we couldn't stop no more.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had to run at night too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And on every Austrian village when we arrived, it looks like they let them know there's Jews arriving.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They came they Hitler Jugend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Hitler Jugend means, in translated, that is the juveniles, the Hitler juveniles, so they were brought up, you know, as Hitlerites.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were waiting for us with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they started shooting, cutting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was jumping over live ones, over wounded ones, over dead ones, only to get away from there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And everybody, not only me, we were running.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You couldn't run away because first of all, you had, on the left hand side, on your breast, you had the yellow star of David, Jude.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Even if you would wanted to take that off, you couldn't hide because, first of all, you looked like a concentration camp guy because you were skinny.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You were a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Not-- they were not dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They ate like horses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Everything what they were robbing, you know, from all the countries wherever they were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They were bringing everything into their father land.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So one day, they took us in the stone mine, where they were mining rocks, building highways.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We had to walk down-- all the way down.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
